{"tid":297551,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇興趣搞個屬於連登仔嘅劇團(2)","createTime":"2017-06-25T14:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T11:24:43.000Z","uid":4210,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35ab357b6e979c0729c508171f0ad3db4be78f38","tid":297551,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"三個月之前開咗第一個招募嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pm我嘅人都幾多<br />\n估唔到連登都幾多對戲劇有興趣嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我哋決定開始第二輪嘅招募<br />\n只要你係對戲劇有興趣有冇經驗都歡迎你入嚟一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於而家乜嘢都係由零開始做起<br />\n所以嚟緊嘅時間我哋會主要會搞workshop先<br />\n主要玩theatre games同埋等大家認識大家，<br />\n會有優良師資帶領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">絲打來的</span></span><br />\n如果可以嘅話我哋最終嘅目標都係大家一齊親手做一套屬於我哋自己嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲諗啲乜嘢喎 心動不如馬上行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣嘅就PM我了解詳情啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTG:hcgfcjk"},{"pid":"9808adb7b7edf1bb89e352cffe9cb4c349b83de5","tid":297551,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94860e0deb1450562a3ecc5da0555ef1e8eab2d6","tid":297551,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4585a026152c1f1ddc2c2fbf06f5fb1aa72cccc0","tid":297551,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa